1
00:04:16,334 --> 00:04:17,634
Stop right there!

2
00:04:23,876 --> 00:04:25,176
Stop!

3
00:04:29,083 --> 00:04:31,051
Huajun, there're Hun soldiers!

4
00:04:47,250 --> 00:04:48,976
Lady, stand behind me.

5
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:51,059
Fight no more and come back with us.

6
00:04:51,083 --> 00:04:52,299
Brother.

7
00:04:52,876 --> 00:04:54,143
What is going on?

8
00:04:54,167 --> 00:04:55,550
Let's talk after we survive this.

9
00:05:17,834 --> 00:05:19,009
Look out!

10
00:05:28,626 --> 00:05:29,884
Watch it!

11
00:06:00,167 --> 00:06:01,425
It's over now.

12
00:06:04,292 --> 00:06:06,383
Lady, what was it about?

13
00:06:22,918 --> 00:06:24,425
I run out of arrows.

14
00:06:24,999 --> 00:06:26,675
What to do?

15
00:06:35,959 --> 00:06:37,134
Go get her.

16
00:07:42,375 --> 00:07:43,550
Stop chasing!

17
00:08:58,375 --> 00:09:00,467
Brother, the Huns will be here soon.

18
00:09:00,584 --> 00:09:02,884
Lady, back to you.

19
00:09:08,626 --> 00:09:09,884
You'd better leave.

20
00:09:10,626 --> 00:09:11,643
What about you?

21
00:09:11,667 --> 00:09:13,299
No need to worry about us.

22
00:09:13,626 --> 00:09:14,926
Take my horse.

23
00:09:15,209 --> 00:09:16,185
He runs fast.

24
00:09:16,209 --> 00:09:18,134
His name is Lei Zhen.

25
00:09:26,417 --> 00:09:27,717
Be careful.

26
00:09:28,292 --> 00:09:29,550
Take care.

27
00:09:44,542 --> 00:09:46,259
Why holding a dandelion?

28
00:10:19,667 --> 00:10:21,560
My knight,
thank you for rescuing me.

29
00:10:21,584 --> 00:10:23,509
Mengyun is grateful.

30
00:10:43,959 --> 00:10:45,884
Do you like dandelions?

31
00:10:53,751 --> 00:10:55,009
Beautiful.

32
00:10:55,876 --> 00:10:57,259
For you.

33
00:11:05,876 --> 00:11:06,976
Professor.

34
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:08,218
Check it out.

35
00:11:08,918 --> 00:11:11,185
Here is the genetic report
of the war horse.

36
00:11:11,209 --> 00:11:12,852
It was a warm-blooded horse.

37
00:11:12,876 --> 00:11:13,894
No wonder.

38
00:11:13,918 --> 00:11:15,634
The size of the horse is so big.

39
00:11:16,667 --> 00:11:17,643
Wang Jing.

40
00:11:17,667 --> 00:11:18,810
What have you got?

41
00:11:18,834 --> 00:11:19,935
Professor.

42
00:11:19,959 --> 00:11:22,101
Part of the war horse
has been excavated.

43
00:11:22,125 --> 00:11:25,143
According to the bridle nose piece

44
00:11:25,167 --> 00:11:26,476
and the saddle,

45
00:11:26,500 --> 00:11:27,852
my assumption is

46
00:11:27,876 --> 00:11:30,018
a mount of a cavalry general
of the Western Han Dynasty.

47
00:11:30,042 --> 00:11:31,592
Strange.

48
00:11:31,918 --> 00:11:34,393
The totem and relief carving of
the mask on this jade pendant

49
00:11:34,417 --> 00:11:36,602
were common in Hunnic culture.

50
00:11:36,626 --> 00:11:38,351
How did such a precious
Hunnic jade pendant

51
00:11:38,375 --> 00:11:40,759
end up on the horse
of the Han people?

52
00:11:43,167 --> 00:11:45,268
Could it be part of the spoils?

53
00:11:45,292 --> 00:11:46,518
It's possible.

54
00:11:46,542 --> 00:11:48,894
Either this jade pendant
was seized by the Han army,

55
00:11:48,918 --> 00:11:51,675
or this war horse
was seized by Huns.

56
00:11:52,042 --> 00:11:53,101
How about...

57
00:11:53,125 --> 00:11:54,310
Look so much alike.

58
00:11:54,334 --> 00:11:55,518
What look alike?

59
00:11:55,542 --> 00:11:57,134
Just now I saw in my dream

60
00:11:57,334 --> 00:11:59,051
a very handsome guy,

61
00:11:59,459 --> 00:12:01,218
but you are not manly like he.

62
00:12:03,584 --> 00:12:05,176
I also dreamed of
a very beautiful woman.

63
00:12:05,417 --> 00:12:06,967
That had to be me.

64
00:12:07,500 --> 00:12:09,134
Don't fool yourself.

65
00:12:09,959 --> 00:12:12,101
Didn't you have something for him?

66
00:12:12,125 --> 00:12:13,143
Go get it.

67
00:12:13,167 --> 00:12:14,685
Hurry up. We don't have time.

68
00:12:14,709 --> 00:12:15,842
Go.

69
00:12:16,167 --> 00:12:17,101
Professor.

70
00:12:17,125 --> 00:12:19,059
Keep working
on the remains of the horse.

71
00:12:19,083 --> 00:12:20,310
I will take this back to the office.

72
00:12:20,334 --> 00:12:21,467
No problem, professor.

73
00:12:21,792 --> 00:12:22,727
Oh yes.

74
00:12:22,751 --> 00:12:23,884
Professor.

75
00:12:24,209 --> 00:12:26,310
Xinran in order to buy you this gift

76
00:12:26,334 --> 00:12:28,176
spent eight hours travelling

77
00:12:28,250 --> 00:12:30,134
back and forth to town downhill.

78
00:12:32,125 --> 00:12:34,467
You wasted that much working time.

79
00:12:37,417 --> 00:12:38,560
Just give it to me.

80
00:12:38,584 --> 00:12:40,051
I'll transfer the money back to you.

81
00:12:42,167 --> 00:12:43,602
If you hadn't overworked
yourself so much,

82
00:12:43,626 --> 00:12:45,259
would I bother to get this for you?

83
00:12:46,167 --> 00:12:48,176
Xinran, I have something
for you too.

84
00:12:50,918 --> 00:12:52,051
What is it?

85
00:12:52,584 --> 00:12:53,560
Take it.

86
00:12:53,584 --> 00:12:55,727
Professor, lunch is on the table
in the lab.

87
00:12:55,751 --> 00:12:56,685
Don't forget to eat it!

88
00:12:56,709 --> 00:12:57,884
I know.

89
00:13:05,167 --> 00:13:06,476
What did he give you?

90
00:13:06,500 --> 00:13:07,685
What else

91
00:13:07,709 --> 00:13:09,218
but lab test list.

92
00:13:10,209 --> 00:13:11,717
One way love is hard.

93
00:13:11,999 --> 00:13:14,435
He really doesn't
care about me, right?

94
00:13:14,459 --> 00:13:15,768
It's easy for a woman
to chase after a man.

95
00:13:15,792 --> 00:13:16,894
How easy?

96
00:13:16,918 --> 00:13:17,894
Look at you.

97
00:13:17,918 --> 00:13:19,310
You wear the same
set of clothes everyday.

98
00:13:19,334 --> 00:13:20,518
Why don't you dress up a little?

99
00:13:20,542 --> 00:13:22,935
Why should I dress up
in an excavation site?

100
00:13:22,959 --> 00:13:23,935
Besides,

101
00:13:23,959 --> 00:13:25,476
I don't think he is that shallow.

102
00:13:25,500 --> 00:13:26,435
Oh yes.

103
00:13:26,459 --> 00:13:27,727
Don't buy me facial masks anymore.

104
00:13:27,751 --> 00:13:30,435
When I put it on my face, it's so
sticky that makes me feel terrible.

105
00:13:30,459 --> 00:13:32,425
Hydration is good for the skin.

106
00:13:32,500 --> 00:13:34,759
Also, Wang Jing's friend
invites us to dinner tonight.

107
00:14:00,918 --> 00:14:02,259
This jade pendant

108
00:14:02,417 --> 00:14:04,717
is a symbol of the sanctuary.

109
00:14:06,000 --> 00:14:08,218
The greatest value of the sanctuary

110
00:14:09,083 --> 00:14:11,383
is not the treasure in it.

111
00:14:12,459 --> 00:14:14,967
Rather, it guards the world's

112
00:14:15,209 --> 00:14:18,342
purest and most virtuous land

113
00:14:18,999 --> 00:14:21,727
that holds our ancesters' and gods'

114
00:14:21,751 --> 00:14:23,342
blessings.

115
00:14:23,999 --> 00:14:27,383
It will bestow blessing upon you.

116
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:42,550
Thank you, my Great Shaman.

117
00:14:45,751 --> 00:14:50,051
I hope you will become my successor.

118
00:15:24,584 --> 00:15:27,643
These are for the benediction
of father's wellness.

119
00:15:27,667 --> 00:15:30,218
My Great Shaman, please bring
them back to the sanctuary.

120
00:15:30,542 --> 00:15:32,467
Dear crown prince, consider it done.

121
00:15:51,292 --> 00:15:52,550
Move on.

122
00:15:53,792 --> 00:15:54,926
Move.

123
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:56,300
Quickly.

124
00:15:56,417 --> 00:15:57,435
Move.

125
00:15:57,459 --> 00:15:58,592
Go.

126
00:16:02,626 --> 00:16:04,134
One by one.

127
00:16:04,999 --> 00:16:05,975
Dear father.

128
00:16:05,999 --> 00:16:07,134
Big brother.

129
00:16:08,083 --> 00:16:09,259
I...

130
00:16:09,417 --> 00:16:12,342
raided the Han people
and took their gold and silk.

131
00:16:12,375 --> 00:16:14,259
I slaughtered everyone in the city.

132
00:16:14,375 --> 00:16:15,935
I also beheaded

133
00:16:15,959 --> 00:16:17,435
the general guarding the fort

134
00:16:17,459 --> 00:16:18,518
and brought it back

135
00:16:18,542 --> 00:16:19,926
as a gift for father.

136
00:16:20,042 --> 00:16:22,550
You rendered outstanding service
this time.

137
00:16:23,918 --> 00:16:25,268
As your father,

138
00:16:25,292 --> 00:16:27,299
how should I reward you?

139
00:16:27,667 --> 00:16:28,810
Father,

140
00:16:28,834 --> 00:16:30,342
I want nothing,

141
00:16:30,417 --> 00:16:32,051
but only wish father would

142
00:16:32,167 --> 00:16:33,476
allow Mengyun

143
00:16:33,500 --> 00:16:34,842
to become my wife.

144
00:16:36,876 --> 00:16:38,259
Mengyun?

145
00:16:40,500 --> 00:16:41,759
Father.

146
00:16:42,584 --> 00:16:43,717
Father.

147
00:16:44,834 --> 00:16:46,218
Mengyun?

148
00:16:47,125 --> 00:16:48,852
Father has already

149
00:16:48,876 --> 00:16:51,259
granted her to your brother.

150
00:16:53,584 --> 00:16:55,218
How about...

151
00:16:55,709 --> 00:16:58,602
all the Han women you took back...

152
00:16:58,626 --> 00:16:59,810
Father.

153
00:16:59,834 --> 00:17:01,509
Grants them all to you.

154
00:17:01,542 --> 00:17:02,759
What do you think?

155
00:17:07,542 --> 00:17:08,759
Yes.

156
00:17:08,834 --> 00:17:11,176
I will do what father says.

157
00:17:11,209 --> 00:17:12,383
Good.

158
00:17:12,876 --> 00:17:14,259
Good.

159
00:17:14,459 --> 00:17:16,393
Father is not well.

160
00:17:16,417 --> 00:17:18,268
You should get some rest now.

161
00:17:18,292 --> 00:17:20,634
Now I will excuse myself.

162
00:17:20,751 --> 00:17:22,218
You get some rest.

163
00:17:30,500 --> 00:17:31,675
Big brother.

164
00:17:37,209 --> 00:17:38,976
You always massacre
the people you subdued.

165
00:17:39,000 --> 00:17:40,602
It is too ruthless.

166
00:17:40,626 --> 00:17:43,560
I'm afraid the Han people
will retaliate.

167
00:17:43,584 --> 00:17:45,592
It will bring disasters
to our people.

168
00:17:47,626 --> 00:17:49,967
I thank the crown prince
for his guidance.

169
00:17:59,167 --> 00:18:01,727
Mother, wait for me
at the agreed place.

170
00:18:01,751 --> 00:18:03,717
I will come and join you.

171
00:18:03,876 --> 00:18:04,975
Let's leave now together.

172
00:18:04,999 --> 00:18:06,976
I must avenge my father.

173
00:18:07,000 --> 00:18:08,509
Let me do it.

174
00:18:09,584 --> 00:18:10,759
Go now.

175
00:18:16,834 --> 00:18:18,009
Be careful.

176
00:18:52,542 --> 00:18:54,134
My daughter.

177
00:19:02,834 --> 00:19:05,051
You killed my father.

178
00:19:07,375 --> 00:19:09,509
I feel deep remorse

179
00:19:11,209 --> 00:19:13,300
for what happened in the past,

180
00:19:17,125 --> 00:19:20,176
but what I did afterwards

181
00:19:20,918 --> 00:19:24,967
was out of love
for you and your mother.

182
00:19:33,125 --> 00:19:34,717
My time

183
00:19:35,667 --> 00:19:37,926
is running out.

184
00:19:38,125 --> 00:19:39,675
Go ahead and do it.

185
00:19:56,542 --> 00:19:57,476
Leave now.

186
00:19:57,500 --> 00:19:59,009
I can still intercede for you.

187
00:19:59,959 --> 00:20:01,759
Think of your mother.

188
00:20:06,667 --> 00:20:08,634
Help.

189
00:20:20,083 --> 00:20:21,467
Father.

190
00:20:21,542 --> 00:20:23,218
Please forgive me.

191
00:20:24,792 --> 00:20:25,926
Big brother.

192
00:20:26,834 --> 00:20:27,967
Father.

193
00:20:28,042 --> 00:20:29,259
What's wrong with father?

194
00:20:33,626 --> 00:20:34,884
Big brother.

195
00:20:35,417 --> 00:20:37,976
This is the crown prince
of your choice.

196
00:20:38,000 --> 00:20:39,634
Let him go.

197
00:20:40,375 --> 00:20:42,018
For you,

198
00:20:42,042 --> 00:20:45,009
I fought battles and risked my life.

199
00:20:45,250 --> 00:20:46,467
But he...

200
00:20:49,167 --> 00:20:50,634
Bit the dust just like that.

201
00:20:51,999 --> 00:20:54,259
You monster.

202
00:20:54,542 --> 00:20:56,518
My son.

203
00:20:56,542 --> 00:20:58,550
Back then the Great Shaman

204
00:20:58,667 --> 00:21:00,383
made a prophecy of divination,

205
00:21:01,042 --> 00:21:03,592
saying I could never become king.

206
00:21:04,500 --> 00:21:06,009
But my dear father,

207
00:21:07,209 --> 00:21:09,310
how come you believe in a prophecy

208
00:21:09,334 --> 00:21:11,009
rather than believe in me?

209
00:21:15,876 --> 00:21:17,550
I'm sorry, father.

210
00:21:19,375 --> 00:21:20,926
I am not being a good son.

211
00:21:23,292 --> 00:21:25,259
Yet

212
00:21:25,375 --> 00:21:26,926
I do this

213
00:21:29,209 --> 00:21:30,717
for our tribes.

214
00:21:49,000 --> 00:21:51,218
Assassin.

215
00:21:51,959 --> 00:21:53,759
Bring Mengyun back.

216
00:22:02,792 --> 00:22:03,727
Professor.

217
00:22:03,751 --> 00:22:05,425
He is my friend, Lei Zhen.

218
00:22:05,459 --> 00:22:06,393
He organizes tonight's party.

219
00:22:06,417 --> 00:22:07,393
Thank you.

220
00:22:07,417 --> 00:22:08,518
The least I can do.

221
00:22:08,542 --> 00:22:10,675
Your huge discovery
is definitely worth celebrating.

222
00:22:11,042 --> 00:22:13,185
My company has developed a new game

223
00:22:13,209 --> 00:22:14,634
called "The Legend of Han and Hun".

224
00:22:14,667 --> 00:22:15,602
Interesting.

225
00:22:15,626 --> 00:22:17,018
When I was in Beijing,

226
00:22:17,042 --> 00:22:18,602
I went to your lecture
on "Wars between Han and Hun".

227
00:22:18,626 --> 00:22:20,643
It inspired me to develop the game.

228
00:22:20,667 --> 00:22:22,351
You are my mentor.

229
00:22:22,375 --> 00:22:23,560
Professor Fang.

230
00:22:23,584 --> 00:22:24,842
Director Wang, how are you?

231
00:22:25,417 --> 00:22:26,643
Please let me introduce.

232
00:22:26,667 --> 00:22:29,393
This is the boy
who discovered the jade pendant,

233
00:22:29,417 --> 00:22:30,550
Baitula, our young friend.

234
00:22:30,751 --> 00:22:32,342
- So pleased to know you.
- Professor, how are you?

235
00:22:33,209 --> 00:22:34,310
Because of you,

236
00:22:34,334 --> 00:22:36,810
we discovered
the horse of an officer

237
00:22:36,834 --> 00:22:38,685
under Western Han dynasty
general Huo Qubing.

238
00:22:38,709 --> 00:22:40,634
- Thank you.
- You're welcome.

239
00:22:41,375 --> 00:22:44,018
He and his family
handed the jade pendant

240
00:22:44,042 --> 00:22:45,393
to the government.

241
00:22:45,417 --> 00:22:46,727
It's a truly commendable act.

242
00:22:46,751 --> 00:22:48,560
I will give you many 'likes'.

243
00:22:48,584 --> 00:22:49,717
By the way, professor,

244
00:22:50,083 --> 00:22:52,393
your application to continue
research on this artifact

245
00:22:52,417 --> 00:22:53,351
has already been approved.

246
00:22:53,375 --> 00:22:54,435
Please sign here.

247
00:22:54,459 --> 00:22:55,643
Thanks.

248
00:22:55,667 --> 00:22:58,975
And we will put part of the artifact

249
00:22:58,999 --> 00:23:01,967
at the museum for public exhibition.

250
00:23:01,999 --> 00:23:04,675
Professor, please come at the time.

251
00:23:04,709 --> 00:23:06,467
Yes, for sure.

252
00:23:07,500 --> 00:23:08,643
Professor,

253
00:23:08,667 --> 00:23:10,393
I especially want to
join your team to learn more.

254
00:23:10,417 --> 00:23:13,509
I also want to hire you
as history advisor for our game.

255
00:23:15,334 --> 00:23:16,467
Well...

256
00:23:19,667 --> 00:23:20,643
This is something
I specially arranged

257
00:23:20,667 --> 00:23:22,218
for everyone to enjoy.

258
00:23:51,417 --> 00:23:52,634
Xinran?

259
00:26:02,042 --> 00:26:04,268
Lady, your dancing with the sword

260
00:26:04,292 --> 00:26:05,550
was really breathtaking.

261
00:26:06,000 --> 00:26:08,759
I wonder if my bow
can be wielded the same way.

262
00:26:12,167 --> 00:26:13,300
Probably not.

263
00:26:16,500 --> 00:26:18,009
Why are you here?

264
00:26:18,584 --> 00:26:21,009
My mother and I
planned to meet here,

265
00:26:21,125 --> 00:26:23,009
but she hasn't shown up yet.

266
00:26:35,876 --> 00:26:37,134
Please pardon me.

267
00:26:40,417 --> 00:26:41,675
Greetings to Great Shaman.

268
00:26:42,417 --> 00:26:43,675
Rise.

269
00:26:45,626 --> 00:26:47,268
Huduna captured your mother.

270
00:26:47,292 --> 00:26:49,884
He uses her as his leverage

271
00:26:51,250 --> 00:26:54,051
to get you into marrying him.

272
00:26:54,542 --> 00:26:56,852
The last thing your mother wants

273
00:26:56,876 --> 00:26:59,299
is for you to repeat her tragedy.

274
00:27:00,209 --> 00:27:01,810
She is my mother.

275
00:27:01,834 --> 00:27:03,842
I must go back and save her.

276
00:27:06,042 --> 00:27:09,176
It seems that
I chose the right heir.

277
00:27:30,250 --> 00:27:31,634
You alright?

278
00:27:31,918 --> 00:27:33,218
Dear knights,

279
00:27:33,500 --> 00:27:34,852
Mengyun still has matters
to attend to.

280
00:27:34,876 --> 00:27:36,550
I will bid farewell now.

281
00:27:36,584 --> 00:27:37,852
Your kindness

282
00:27:37,876 --> 00:27:39,425
will always be remembered
by Mengyun.

283
00:28:11,751 --> 00:28:13,259
You can really sleep.

284
00:28:13,459 --> 00:28:14,717
Everyone's gone.

285
00:28:16,167 --> 00:28:18,259
Professor, I had a dream.

286
00:28:18,375 --> 00:28:19,560
I dreamed of a young man

287
00:28:19,584 --> 00:28:21,009
who looked a lot like you.

288
00:28:22,083 --> 00:28:23,884
I also dreamed of
a very beautiful woman.

289
00:28:24,709 --> 00:28:27,101
The beauty in real life
was so mad at you that she left.

290
00:28:27,125 --> 00:28:28,685
Leave alone that beauty
in your dream.

291
00:28:28,709 --> 00:28:30,976
She dressed up and danced for you,

292
00:28:31,000 --> 00:28:32,310
but you fell asleep.

293
00:28:32,334 --> 00:28:34,009
Go now to see her.

294
00:28:34,834 --> 00:28:36,342
OK, I go now.

295
00:28:38,918 --> 00:28:40,926
Your coat. It's cold up there.

296
00:28:40,999 --> 00:28:42,259
OK, thank you, professor.

297
00:28:49,834 --> 00:28:52,176
Xinran, here you are.

298
00:28:52,292 --> 00:28:53,675
You finally woke up.

299
00:28:56,626 --> 00:28:58,134
It's so cold up here.

300
00:28:58,959 --> 00:29:01,299
Xinran, I didn't realize
you could dance so well.

301
00:29:04,125 --> 00:29:06,852
Well, you watched?

302
00:29:06,876 --> 00:29:08,176
I was watching.

303
00:29:08,667 --> 00:29:11,009
Surely, with a loud snoring?

304
00:29:16,459 --> 00:29:17,592
Xinran.

305
00:29:17,667 --> 00:29:18,935
Actually without glasses

306
00:29:18,959 --> 00:29:20,884
and in a skirt,
you look really good.

307
00:29:23,626 --> 00:29:24,967
You are so shallow.

308
00:29:26,542 --> 00:29:29,051
Did you use the facial masks
I bought you?

309
00:29:30,000 --> 00:29:31,299
Oh, those were facial masks?

310
00:29:32,459 --> 00:29:35,634
Did you look at the other things?

311
00:29:36,918 --> 00:29:38,310
Work has been busy lately.

312
00:29:38,334 --> 00:29:39,351
So...

313
00:29:39,375 --> 00:29:40,717
I forgot.

314
00:29:44,542 --> 00:29:48,185
I often wonder
other than work in your mind

315
00:29:48,209 --> 00:29:49,810
could you think of anything else?

316
00:29:49,834 --> 00:29:51,009
Such as?

317
00:29:51,083 --> 00:29:52,018
Such as

318
00:29:52,042 --> 00:29:54,059
caring about the people around you.

319
00:29:54,083 --> 00:29:56,218
OK, I'll pay more attention to it
in the future.

320
00:29:56,959 --> 00:29:58,518
Since the Qin Dynasty,

321
00:29:58,542 --> 00:30:01,467
the Huns had repeatedly invaded
China's mainland.

322
00:30:01,626 --> 00:30:03,143
During the reign of
Emperor Wu of Han Dynasty,

323
00:30:03,167 --> 00:30:05,894
Shandan Military Horse Farm
was established.

324
00:30:05,918 --> 00:30:08,351
Since then we had the cavalry force

325
00:30:08,375 --> 00:30:09,643
to fight against the Huns.

326
00:30:09,667 --> 00:30:10,685
Shandan Military Horse Farm

327
00:30:10,709 --> 00:30:12,894
was founded by Huo Qubing, right?

328
00:30:12,918 --> 00:30:14,051
Correct.

329
00:30:14,334 --> 00:30:15,602
What you all see now

330
00:30:15,626 --> 00:30:18,675
is a specimen model
of a Celestial Horse.

331
00:30:22,918 --> 00:30:25,926
I still think only a white horse
is fit for a prince.

332
00:30:26,459 --> 00:30:28,643
Who named you Lei Zhen?

333
00:30:28,667 --> 00:30:29,842
My mother.

334
00:30:32,751 --> 00:30:33,894
What?

335
00:30:33,918 --> 00:30:35,550
Could've been Lei Zhenzi.

336
00:30:39,709 --> 00:30:41,226
Did you know how the word "champion"

337
00:30:41,250 --> 00:30:42,926
becomes widely known?

338
00:30:44,209 --> 00:30:45,342
Please tell us.

339
00:30:45,584 --> 00:30:46,717
Let's hear it from professor.

340
00:30:47,542 --> 00:30:49,059
Seventeen-year-old Huo Qubing

341
00:30:49,083 --> 00:30:50,518
followed his uncle Wei Qing

342
00:30:50,542 --> 00:30:52,176
to fight the Huns
for the first time.

343
00:30:52,709 --> 00:30:55,101
Wei Qing only gave him 800 horsemen.

344
00:30:55,125 --> 00:30:56,976
He went deep
into the enemy territory

345
00:30:57,000 --> 00:30:59,051
straight to the rear of the Huns...

346
00:32:00,542 --> 00:32:01,976
The Huns,

347
00:32:02,000 --> 00:32:05,467
they took my daughter.

348
00:32:34,751 --> 00:32:36,259
Take good care of him.

349
00:32:50,209 --> 00:32:51,383
General,

350
00:32:51,417 --> 00:32:53,717
the Hunnic tribe was found
near the river valley.

351
00:32:55,709 --> 00:32:57,176
March through the night.

352
00:32:57,209 --> 00:32:59,467
We must bring our people back home!

353
00:34:03,209 --> 00:34:05,051
Help!

354
00:34:06,999 --> 00:34:08,643
Please let me go.

355
00:34:08,667 --> 00:34:10,967
Let me go.

356
00:34:12,999 --> 00:34:14,259
Zhao Zhan, Huajun.

357
00:34:16,000 --> 00:34:17,800
You each bring your men.

358
00:34:19,083 --> 00:34:21,176
We will raid them
from three directions

359
00:34:21,459 --> 00:34:22,926
to get them off-guard.

360
00:34:22,999 --> 00:34:24,218
Command received.

361
00:34:49,417 --> 00:34:50,842
Lei Zhen?

362
00:35:36,292 --> 00:35:37,592
What about my mother?

363
00:35:38,542 --> 00:35:40,467
You promised to let her go.

364
00:36:00,667 --> 00:36:01,800
Let's go.

365
00:36:06,292 --> 00:36:07,717
Lei Zhen.

366
00:36:49,584 --> 00:36:50,717
Over there.

367
00:36:56,167 --> 00:36:58,967
Kill them all.

368
00:36:59,751 --> 00:37:01,342
Enemy is here.

369
00:37:26,167 --> 00:37:27,383
Free the people.

370
00:37:41,000 --> 00:37:43,051
Tell me where the sanctuary is.

371
00:37:43,834 --> 00:37:46,134
Only the Great Shaman knows.

372
00:37:46,292 --> 00:37:47,759
The Hans are here.

373
00:39:57,292 --> 00:39:58,842
Guard the king.

374
00:40:11,375 --> 00:40:12,926
Block him.

375
00:40:33,000 --> 00:40:34,218
Lei Zhen.

376
00:41:03,709 --> 00:41:04,842
Hold it.

377
00:41:05,959 --> 00:41:07,299
General's order.

378
00:41:07,334 --> 00:41:08,884
Spare women, children,
elderly and infants.

379
00:41:09,042 --> 00:41:10,592
Those who surrender will live.

380
00:41:11,375 --> 00:41:12,509
Got it.

381
00:41:19,792 --> 00:41:20,926
Come with us.

382
00:41:26,167 --> 00:41:27,675
- Mother.
- My daughter.

383
00:41:29,542 --> 00:41:30,884
Are you alright?

384
00:41:30,999 --> 00:41:32,176
I'm fine.

385
00:41:45,292 --> 00:41:46,550
Mother.

386
00:41:49,209 --> 00:41:50,425
My daughter.

387
00:41:50,500 --> 00:41:52,967
You must go back to Han land.

388
00:41:53,167 --> 00:41:54,383
Do your best

389
00:41:54,876 --> 00:41:56,425
to live your life.

390
00:41:59,500 --> 00:42:00,967
Mother.

391
00:42:03,083 --> 00:42:04,259
Mother.

392
00:42:04,459 --> 00:42:06,259
Mother.

393
00:42:12,417 --> 00:42:14,884
Mother.

394
00:42:21,042 --> 00:42:22,717
Mother.

395
00:42:49,375 --> 00:42:50,550
Whoever

396
00:42:51,167 --> 00:42:53,592
surrenders himself to Han Courts

397
00:42:53,834 --> 00:42:55,675
will be treated with mercy.

398
00:43:09,000 --> 00:43:12,592
My father was a Hun general
who pledged allegiance to Han.

399
00:43:13,876 --> 00:43:16,299
King Tudie invaded the city
under his guard

400
00:43:16,918 --> 00:43:18,634
and massacred everyone
including my father.

401
00:43:20,375 --> 00:43:22,300
To ensure my safety,

402
00:43:23,918 --> 00:43:26,467
my mother gave herself
to King Tudie.

403
00:43:27,209 --> 00:43:30,051
She just wanted me to live well.

404
00:43:32,125 --> 00:43:34,009
The best time of my life

405
00:43:34,292 --> 00:43:37,009
was when we two
looked for dandelions.

406
00:43:37,999 --> 00:43:40,467
But now she's gone.

407
00:43:43,292 --> 00:43:44,425
Mengyun,

408
00:43:44,584 --> 00:43:46,560
will you go back
to the garrison with me

409
00:43:46,584 --> 00:43:48,509
and help us train
the horses for battles?

410
00:43:50,334 --> 00:43:51,592
Will you be there?

411
00:43:51,667 --> 00:43:52,967
I will.

412
00:43:58,918 --> 00:43:59,976
Mother.

413
00:44:00,000 --> 00:44:02,300
I can finally go back to Han land.

414
00:44:08,542 --> 00:44:10,467
Zhao Zhan, Hua Jun.

415
00:44:10,500 --> 00:44:14,051
You two went through hardships
and brought back all these stallion

416
00:44:14,417 --> 00:44:16,967
will greatly strengthen our cavalry.

417
00:44:18,209 --> 00:44:20,218
You have done great service
for Han Dynasty.

418
00:44:20,626 --> 00:44:22,476
Your efforts are appreciated.

419
00:44:22,500 --> 00:44:24,259
We only did what we should do.

420
00:44:27,250 --> 00:44:28,935
What a nice Ferghana horse!

421
00:44:28,959 --> 00:44:30,059
Height is good.

422
00:44:30,083 --> 00:44:31,435
Limbs are slender.

423
00:44:31,459 --> 00:44:32,393
Skin is thin.

424
00:44:32,417 --> 00:44:34,009
Face is small and neck is high.

425
00:44:34,417 --> 00:44:35,592
Good horse!

426
00:46:07,125 --> 00:46:08,299
Big brother.

427
00:46:08,542 --> 00:46:09,643
I got a letter from home.

428
00:46:09,667 --> 00:46:10,810
My father found a job for me

429
00:46:10,834 --> 00:46:12,425
at the prime minister's bureau.

430
00:46:12,584 --> 00:46:14,009
When this battle is over,

431
00:46:14,042 --> 00:46:15,509
I will go work there.

432
00:46:17,083 --> 00:46:18,383
You might as well.

433
00:46:18,709 --> 00:46:20,051
Three generations in your family

434
00:46:20,083 --> 00:46:21,351
have held office
in the imperial court.

435
00:46:21,375 --> 00:46:22,976
You are the only son in the family.

436
00:46:23,000 --> 00:46:26,342
People say one should not travel
far from parents' side.

437
00:46:44,334 --> 00:46:46,467
Big brother, ever thought
of starting a family?

438
00:46:55,876 --> 00:46:57,009
Family?

439
00:46:58,459 --> 00:47:00,300
I know not what a family is
since small.

440
00:47:00,667 --> 00:47:02,550
I was born at the frontier.

441
00:47:03,334 --> 00:47:04,800
The Huns

442
00:47:05,334 --> 00:47:07,383
destroyed my family.

443
00:47:07,999 --> 00:47:09,550
As long as the Hun
military threat exists,

444
00:47:09,626 --> 00:47:11,634
there is no talk of
starting a family.

445
00:47:12,334 --> 00:47:13,800
Indeed.

446
00:47:14,083 --> 00:47:16,342
To extinguish such threats
is top priority.

447
00:47:24,834 --> 00:47:25,967
The general is here.

448
00:47:28,626 --> 00:47:29,685
General.

449
00:47:29,709 --> 00:47:30,602
General.

450
00:47:30,626 --> 00:47:33,018
The general has bred excellent
war horses for the country.

451
00:47:33,042 --> 00:47:36,634
We now also have
our own cavalry regiments.

452
00:47:37,250 --> 00:47:39,467
The Huns repeatedly invaded
our Han territory.

453
00:47:39,876 --> 00:47:41,842
We are Han soldiers.

454
00:47:42,167 --> 00:47:43,467
Hun's

455
00:47:43,542 --> 00:47:44,810
repeated offences

456
00:47:44,834 --> 00:47:46,218
must be eliminated.

457
00:47:46,626 --> 00:47:48,842
I believe that in the future

458
00:47:49,125 --> 00:47:51,467
in this land of China,

459
00:47:51,667 --> 00:47:53,268
there will be peace and prosperity.

460
00:47:53,292 --> 00:47:56,051
People will live and work
in peace with contentment.

461
00:48:10,459 --> 00:48:12,602
Huo Qubing built his fame
in this battle

462
00:48:12,626 --> 00:48:14,101
with military achievement
beyond compare.

463
00:48:14,125 --> 00:48:16,602
Emperor Wu named him
"Duke of Champion"

464
00:48:16,626 --> 00:48:19,051
This is how the word "champion"
becomes widely known

465
00:48:19,626 --> 00:48:22,185
Although Huo Qubing
lived a short life

466
00:48:22,209 --> 00:48:24,727
he repeatedly inflicted
heavy losses on the Huns.

467
00:48:24,751 --> 00:48:25,975
For Han Dynasty,

468
00:48:25,999 --> 00:48:28,602
he formed
a superior army of cavalry.

469
00:48:28,626 --> 00:48:29,852
Later, the Han Dynasty

470
00:48:29,876 --> 00:48:31,935
was able to
open up the Hexi Corridor,

471
00:48:31,959 --> 00:48:33,602
and established
the Western Regions Protectorate

472
00:48:33,626 --> 00:48:36,009
to consolidate ruling
over the Xinjiang region.

473
00:48:36,125 --> 00:48:37,884
Huo laid the foundation
for all those to happen.

474
00:48:38,834 --> 00:48:39,967
Professor.

475
00:48:40,083 --> 00:48:41,518
The general on the white horse

476
00:48:41,542 --> 00:48:42,560
doesn't he look like Wang Jing?

477
00:48:42,584 --> 00:48:44,051
Look like Wang Jing?

478
00:48:48,042 --> 00:48:49,259
Not really.

479
00:48:51,167 --> 00:48:52,101
You have only Wang Jing
on your mind.

480
00:48:52,125 --> 00:48:53,509
- Professor.
- No, I...

481
00:48:55,375 --> 00:48:56,685
This is really something.

482
00:48:56,709 --> 00:48:58,842
So many different shapes
of gold nuggets.

483
00:48:58,876 --> 00:49:01,009
This is Horseshoe gold nugget.

484
00:49:01,667 --> 00:49:02,643
You tell me

485
00:49:02,667 --> 00:49:05,727
with all those gold
contributed from Han,

486
00:49:05,751 --> 00:49:07,300
where could the Huns
have stored them?

487
00:49:07,709 --> 00:49:08,727
It is recorded that

488
00:49:08,751 --> 00:49:10,393
Huo Qubing once seized

489
00:49:10,417 --> 00:49:12,101
Hun's golden statue
for worship of Heaven.

490
00:49:12,125 --> 00:49:14,560
Would it be possible
that the gold and treasures

491
00:49:14,584 --> 00:49:17,259
were sent to
Hun's sanctuary for worship?

492
00:49:17,751 --> 00:49:20,976
Up till now, no Hun's sanctuary
has ever been discovered.

493
00:49:21,000 --> 00:49:21,935
However,

494
00:49:21,959 --> 00:49:22,894
since you develop games,

495
00:49:22,918 --> 00:49:25,476
feel free to use your creativity.

496
00:49:25,500 --> 00:49:28,101
Surely I wanted
the treasure hunting element added.

497
00:49:28,125 --> 00:49:29,976
If only you could lead us

498
00:49:30,000 --> 00:49:31,894
to find Hun's sanctuary,

499
00:49:31,918 --> 00:49:33,967
that would be so cool.

500
00:49:35,292 --> 00:49:36,800
Too difficult.

501
00:49:37,000 --> 00:49:38,509
It's so beautiful.

502
00:49:38,959 --> 00:49:40,259
You have good taste.

503
00:49:40,918 --> 00:49:41,894
For this bracelet,

504
00:49:41,918 --> 00:49:43,310
we copy the exact design
and size of the original

505
00:49:43,334 --> 00:49:45,268
to make gold replica souvenir.

506
00:49:45,292 --> 00:49:46,800
Definitely great value for money.

507
00:49:48,334 --> 00:49:50,800
It's perfect for me, isn't it?

508
00:49:51,042 --> 00:49:52,675
Price of gold has risen
so much lately.

509
00:50:01,792 --> 00:50:02,926
Professor.

510
00:50:03,083 --> 00:50:04,101
I have a good friend

511
00:50:04,125 --> 00:50:05,185
who is a shamanic scholar.

512
00:50:05,209 --> 00:50:06,602
It so happens that
he is recently back to China.

513
00:50:06,626 --> 00:50:07,852
He knows shamanic culture

514
00:50:07,876 --> 00:50:10,018
and the history of Hun very well.

515
00:50:10,042 --> 00:50:11,518
He invited us to visit him.

516
00:50:11,542 --> 00:50:13,685
We can talk about the totem
on the jade pendant.

517
00:50:13,709 --> 00:50:15,059
We can surely compare notes.

518
00:50:15,083 --> 00:50:16,143
I will arrange a time.

519
00:50:16,167 --> 00:50:17,059
OK, go ahead.

520
00:50:17,083 --> 00:50:18,059
OK.

521
00:50:18,083 --> 00:50:19,226
What to do next?

522
00:50:19,250 --> 00:50:20,518
- Let's have tea.
- Great.

523
00:50:20,542 --> 00:50:22,134
- Let's go for tea.
- After you.

524
00:50:23,500 --> 00:50:24,560
Gold is expensive.

525
00:50:24,584 --> 00:50:25,602
Forget it.

526
00:50:25,626 --> 00:50:26,800
Let's go.

527
00:50:28,334 --> 00:50:29,926
Yes, too expensive.

528
00:50:42,876 --> 00:50:44,425
What's the fuss?

529
00:50:45,584 --> 00:50:46,717
Professor.

530
00:50:46,834 --> 00:50:48,009
This mask is ok.

531
00:50:48,584 --> 00:50:50,476
Xinran taught me how to use it.

532
00:50:50,500 --> 00:50:52,310
The tacky wet feeling
is uncomfortable.

533
00:50:52,334 --> 00:50:54,051
Professor, can I take it off?

534
00:50:54,417 --> 00:50:55,393
Hydrate your skin is good.

535
00:50:55,417 --> 00:50:56,675
It's gppd for you.

536
00:50:57,375 --> 00:50:59,259
What do you want from me
at this early hour?

537
00:51:00,209 --> 00:51:01,894
I drew a picture
with artificial intelligence.

538
00:51:01,918 --> 00:51:04,467
This is the woman in my dream.

539
00:51:05,751 --> 00:51:06,685
She looks so much like...

540
00:51:06,709 --> 00:51:07,842
Like who?

541
00:51:08,083 --> 00:51:10,518
The one I saw in my dream.

542
00:51:10,542 --> 00:51:11,884
Professor, how can it be possible?

543
00:51:12,000 --> 00:51:14,009
The same person
appeared in our dreams.

544
00:51:14,292 --> 00:51:16,643
Maybe we've been working
on the jade pendant.

545
00:51:16,667 --> 00:51:18,435
We did the same research work,

546
00:51:18,459 --> 00:51:20,592
so we had the same dream.

547
00:51:22,125 --> 00:51:23,059
Professor.

548
00:51:23,083 --> 00:51:25,342
Why do I feel like they are

549
00:51:25,417 --> 00:51:27,759
my memories
of another time and space?

550
00:51:28,000 --> 00:51:28,976
Dreams

551
00:51:29,000 --> 00:51:30,727
are more than the working
of brain's memory system

552
00:51:30,751 --> 00:51:31,935
in our dormant condition.

553
00:51:31,959 --> 00:51:32,975
In fact,

554
00:51:32,999 --> 00:51:35,592
the brain's ability to create
is also functioning.

555
00:51:35,834 --> 00:51:38,884
That's why dreams are also
both fantasy and reality.

556
00:51:40,667 --> 00:51:41,727
A dream is not reality.

557
00:51:41,751 --> 00:51:44,634
We still have to come back
to the real world.

558
00:51:45,500 --> 00:51:47,310
Okay, professor, I'm back.

559
00:51:47,334 --> 00:51:48,467
I have things to do.

560
00:51:49,042 --> 00:51:50,143
Where are you going?

561
00:51:50,167 --> 00:51:51,967
I'll go find Xinran.

562
00:51:53,167 --> 00:51:54,300
Man

563
00:51:54,334 --> 00:51:55,967
should take the initiative.

564
00:51:56,000 --> 00:51:57,176
OK.

565
