more about it.

657
00:59:16,459 --> 00:59:17,592
Thank you.

658
00:59:40,834 --> 00:59:42,675
In shamanic culture,

659
00:59:43,000 --> 00:59:45,634
this is the oldest
seven-star god totem.

660
00:59:46,042 --> 00:59:47,935
Since this jade pendant
was unearthed,

661
00:59:47,959 --> 00:59:49,560
every night the professor and I

662
00:59:49,584 --> 00:59:51,059
dream of the one same person.

663
00:59:51,083 --> 00:59:52,643
But not me.

664
00:59:52,667 --> 00:59:54,009
Besides...

665
00:59:54,667 --> 00:59:56,176
There are objects

666
00:59:56,375 --> 00:59:59,051
