for our Han army has arrived.

756
01:04:28,000 --> 01:04:29,842
I want to join
the ring pommel sword regiment.

757
01:04:30,918 --> 01:04:33,425
We are soldiers
to defend our homeland.

758
01:04:33,918 --> 01:04:35,383
