788
01:07:36,709 --> 01:07:38,299
or invade our land any more.

789
01:07:47,209 --> 01:07:48,675
Gaolan Mountain

790
01:07:48,709 --> 01:07:50,509
will be Han soldiers'

791
01:07:52,334 --> 01:07:54,342
burial ground.

792
01:07:59,918 --> 01:08:01,550
The peace of our country and home

793
01:08:01,751 --> 01:08:03,310
is forged by heroes.

794
01:08:03,334 --> 01:08:06,018
The peace of our country and home
is forged by heroes.

795
01:08:06,042 --> 01:08:08,051
Forged by heroes.

796
01:08:08,500 --> 01:08:09,675
Charge!

797
01:08:18,083 --> 01:08:19,342
Ring pommel sword regiment.

798
01:09:00,834 --> 01:09:02,717
Get around and outflank them.

799
01:09:58,042 --> 01:09:59,467
Attack from both sides.

800
01:09:59,918 --> 01:10:02,259
Attack from both sides.

801
01:10:10,167 --> 01:10:11,351
Shoot arrows.

802
01:10:11,375 --> 01:10:12,592
Shoot.

803
01:10:23,918 --> 01:10:25,299
Shoot.

804
01:10:35,459 --> 01:10:36,926
Shoot.

805
01:10:46,918 --> 01:10:48,134
Move back.

806
01:12:27,250 --> 01:12:28,185
Huduna is defeated.

807
01:12:28,209 --> 01:12:30,176
My lord, should we advance?

808
01:12:31,209 --> 01:12:32,351
Kill them all.

809
01:12:32,375 --> 01:12:33,592
Kill them all.

810
01:12:45,834 --> 01:12:46,935
Retreat.

811
01:12:46,959 --> 01:12:48,092
Retreat.

812
01:12:58,000 --> 01:12:59,467
Retreat.

813
01:13:00,250 --> 01:13:01,425
Let's go.

814
01:13:05,167 --> 01:13:06,342
Get into position.

815
01:17:23,292 --> 01:17:24,509
General.

816
01:17:25,626 --> 01:17:27,842
Go get them.

817
01:17:37,959 --> 01:17:39,092
Let's go.

818
01:18:00,500 --> 01:18:01,967
Medic.

819
01:18:02,584 --> 01:18:03,926
Medic.

820
01:18:03,999 --> 01:18:04,894
General.

821
01:18:04,918 --> 01:18:05,975
General.

822
