- Let's get out of here.
- Wang Jing, I'll wait for you.

1133
01:50:10,999 --> 01:50:11,976
Professor.

1134
01:50:12,000 --> 01:50:13,018
Why are you back?

1135
01:50:13,042 --> 01:50:14,383
To help you.

1136
01:50:15,083 --> 01:50:16,259
Stay behind me.

1137
01:50:17,042 --> 01:50:18,299
I'll be waiting for you.

1138
01:50:19,584 --> 01:50:21,550
Don't look. Get down.

1139
01:50:24,292 --> 01:50:25,185
Lei Zhen.

1140
01:50:25,209 --> 01:50:26,759
- Lei Zhen.
- Lei Zhen.

1141
01:50:32,500 --> 01:50:33,967
- No more bullets.
- What to do?

1142
01:50:34,167 --> 01:50:35,300
Go over there.

1143
01:50:35,667 --> 01:50:36,976
Kill them all.

1144
01:50:37,000 --> 01:50:38,176
Copy that.

1145
01:50:45,459 --> 01:50:46,592
Zhou Bin.

1146
01:50:46,751 --> 01:50:47,884
Boss.

1147
01:50:48,125 --> 01:50:49,602
We cannot blow up these artifacts.

1148
01:50:49,626 --> 01:50:50,727
My baby has just been born.

1149
01:50:50,751 --> 01:50:52,176
I don't want to go to prison
for the rest of my life...

1150
01:50:55,751 --> 01:50:56,926
Let me see.

1151
01:50:57,000 --> 01:50:57,975
Gently.

1152
01:50:57,999 --> 01:50:59,300
Press it tightly with your hand.

1153
01:50:59,834 --> 01:51:01,550
Luckily there are no organs
in the legs.

1154
01:51:04,959 --> 01:51:06,092
Herbert.

1155
01:51:06,167 --> 01:51:08,134
Do you think there is
only golden statue here?

1156
01:51:08,209 --> 01:51:09,768
The treasures of the Hun
are also here.

1157
01:51:09,792 --> 01:51:10,727
Where?

1158
01:51:10,751 --> 01:51:12,685
The answer is in the writing
on the wall outside.

1159
01:51:12,709 --> 01:51:14,425
The writing on the wall?

1160
01:51:21,375 --> 01:51:22,800
You have my attention now.

1161
01:51:30,709 --> 01:51:31,842
Tell me.

1162
01:51:32,209 --> 01:51:33,342
Xinran.

1163
01:51:33,999 --> 01:51:35,425
Is Lei Zhen OK?

1164
01:51:36,417 --> 01:51:37,476
He is fine.

1165
01:51:37,500 --> 01:51:39,509
He only got shot twice.

1166
01:51:40,292 --> 01:51:41,592
Professor.

1167
01:51:41,959 --> 01:51:43,383
I'm waiting.

1168
01:51:44,042 --> 01:51:46,092
You let them go first,
then I tell you.

1169
01:51:47,042 --> 01:51:48,342
Why should I trust you?

1170
01:51:52,959 --> 01:51:54,092
That's it.

1171
01:52:23,334 --> 01:52:24,467
Professor.

1172
01:52:24,542 --> 01:52:25,842
Give it up.

1173
01:52:27,667 --> 01:52:28,800
Right.

1174
01:52:28,918 --> 01:52:30,051
Let the gas out.

1175
01:53:07,667 --> 01:53:09,675
Don't hack me.

1176
01:54:13,292 --> 01:54:15,299
Stay away from me.
Don't come any closer.

1177
01:54:32,876 --> 01:54:33,810
Professor.

1178
01:54:33,834 --> 01:54:35,226
Take them out of here
and call the police.

1179
01:54:35,250 --> 01:54:36,310
OK.

1180
01:54:36,334 --> 01:54:37,226
Hurry.

1181
01:54:37,250 --> 01:54:38,926
- Xinran.
- Wang Jing.

1182
01:54:40,626 --> 01:54:42,351
Lei Zhen lost lots of blood,
and must get him to hospital.

1183
01:54:42,375 --> 01:54:43,393
- I can't get him up.
- I'll help you.

1184
01:54:43,417 --> 01:54:44,351
Okay.

1185
01:54:44,375 --> 01:54:45,509
No one can leave.

1186
01:54:49,667 --> 01:54:50,800
Wang Jing.

1187
01:54:57,083 --> 01:55:00,176
Why did you block the arrow for me?

1188
01:55:00,375 --> 01:55:01,727
I saw you were in danger.

1189
01:55:01,751 --> 01:55:02,884
Then I...

1190
01:55:03,709 --> 01:55:05,051
It hurts? Where?

1191
01:55:05,375 --> 01:55:06,717
Where does it hurt?

1192
01:55:08,500 --> 01:55:10,092
Nowhere in particular.

1193
01:55:14,125 --> 01:55:15,226
My bag!

1194
01:55:15,250 --> 01:55:16,675
My leg!

1195
01:55:20,334 --> 01:55:21,268
You lost so much blood.

1196
01:55:21,292 --> 01:55:22,476
Why didn't you say
that your leg hurts?

1197
01:55:22,500 --> 01:55:23,675
Call the police.

1198
01:55:40,375 --> 01:55:41,509
Professor.

1199
01:56:23,167 --> 01:56:24,509
Are you okay?

1200
01:56:41,792 --> 01:56:43,051
Professor.

1201
01:56:43,083 --> 01:56:45,342
No one can defy fate.

1202
01:56:48,834 --> 01:56:50,509
What is mine

1203
01:56:50,584 --> 01:56:52,176
shall be mine.

1204
01:57:35,792 --> 01:57:37,300
Hang in there.

1205
01:58:16,918 --> 01:58:18,051
Here.

1206
01:58:18,167 --> 01:58:19,509
Drink some water.

1207
01:58:20,999 --> 01:58:22,550
Brother-in-law, let's head back.

1208
01:58:23,209 --> 01:58:24,675
It's so cold.

1209
01:58:26,042 --> 01:58:27,218
Are you cold?

1210
01:58:27,500 --> 01:58:28,717
I think it's not that bad.

1211
01:58:34,918 --> 01:58:36,393
Here it comes.

1212
01:58:36,417 --> 01:58:38,351
You see?

1213
01:58:38,375 --> 01:58:40,685
Perseverence will pay off.

1214
01:58:40,709 --> 01:58:41,884
This fish is big.

1215
01:58:50,459 --> 01:58:51,560
It's a big fish.

1216
01:58:51,584 --> 01:58:52,476
Keep going!

1217
01:58:52,500 --> 01:58:53,800
Come on!

1218
01:58:57,417 --> 01:58:58,351
A big one.

1219
01:58:58,375 --> 01:59:00,342
It weighs at least 50-80 catties.

1220
01:59:16,167 --> 01:59:17,268
It got off my hook.

1221
01:59:17,292 --> 01:59:18,592
Not really.

1222
01:59:19,125 --> 01:59:20,467
The fish is still here.

1223
01:59:22,500 --> 01:59:24,467
I've never seen
this kind of fish lips.

1224
01:59:26,167 --> 01:59:27,185
Don't move.

1225
01:59:27,209 --> 01:59:28,467
It has teeth.

1226
01:59:29,125 --> 01:59:30,800
Help.

1227
01:59:31,334 --> 01:59:32,935
It speaks human language?

1228
01:59:32,959 --> 01:59:34,092
Help.

1229
01:59:34,125 --> 01:59:35,509
I think it said help.

1230
01:59:36,751 --> 01:59:38,018
Help.

1231
01:59:38,042 --> 01:59:39,185
Pal, how did you get in?

1232
01:59:39,209 --> 01:59:40,518
Where are you swimming to?

1233
01:59:40,542 --> 01:59:42,476
- Why are you chatting with him?
- Get him out.

1234
01:59:42,500 --> 01:59:44,134
Right.

1235
01:59:46,626 --> 01:59:47,768
Help.

1236
01:59:47,792 --> 01:59:48,768
Help.

1237
01:59:48,792 --> 01:59:49,768
Brother-in-law, hurry up.

1238
01:59:49,792 --> 01:59:51,176
Hang in there.

1239
01:59:55,459 --> 01:59:57,299
There is still no signal.

1240
02:00:00,959 --> 02:00:01,894
Xinran.

1241
02:00:01,918 --> 02:00:03,018
If you're my girlfriend,

1242
02:00:03,042 --> 02:00:04,675
you take Lei Zhen out of here now.

1243
02:00:05,000 --> 02:00:06,176
What about you?

1244
02:00:06,209 --> 02:00:07,842
I'll go find the professor.

1245
02:00:08,876 --> 02:00:09,810
Cannot leave him there
all by himself.

1246
02:00:09,834 --> 02:00:12,310
Wang Jing.
We agreed we would stick together.

1247
02:00:12,334 --> 02:00:13,467
Wang Jing.

1248
02:00:14,000 --> 02:00:15,176
Wang Jing.

1249
02:00:20,417 --> 02:00:22,425
Help.

1250
02:00:26,042 --> 02:00:28,342
Help.

1251
02:00:29,918 --> 02:00:31,926
Help.

1252
02:00:41,167 --> 02:00:42,976
Hurry up, get the quilt.

1253
02:00:43,000 --> 02:00:44,299
Quickly.

1254
02:00:52,751 --> 02:00:54,051
Over here, please.

1255
02:00:54,459 --> 02:00:56,051
Wang Jing, you're so handsome.

1256
02:00:56,626 --> 02:00:57,560
Professor Fang.

1257
02:00:57,584 --> 02:00:59,351
In your story "A Legend",

1258
02:00:59,375 --> 02:01:01,143
the tragic romance
echoes in one's heart.

1259
02:01:01,167 --> 02:01:02,226
Simply splendid.

1260
02:01:02,250 --> 02:01:03,717
I develop games.

1261
02:01:03,751 --> 02:01:06,299
Can I buy the game rights
to your book?

1262
02:01:06,459 --> 02:01:08,226
We have developed the game.

1263
02:01:08,250 --> 02:01:09,185
We need nothing

1264
02:01:09,209 --> 02:01:10,310
but funding.

1265
02:01:10,334 --> 02:01:12,300
That's easy. I have money.

1266
02:01:12,334 --> 02:01:13,560
Wonderful!

1267
02:01:13,584 --> 02:01:14,476
Let's talk over there.

1268
02:01:14,500 --> 02:01:16,059
- Can you walk?
- I can.

1269
02:01:16,083 --> 02:01:17,300
- Good.
- Let's go.

1270
02:01:17,417 --> 02:01:18,560
Xinran, his book.

1271
02:01:18,584 --> 02:01:19,560
Sir, your book.

1272
02:01:19,584 --> 02:01:20,476
Professor Fang.

1273
02:01:20,500 --> 02:01:21,393
Hello.

1274
02:01:21,417 --> 02:01:22,759
Mr. Wang Jing.

1275
02:01:22,876 --> 02:01:24,727
The story of Zhao Zhan and Mengyun

1276
02:01:24,751 --> 02:01:26,435
has such a sad ending.

1277
02:01:26,459 --> 02:01:27,810
I feel awful.

1278
02:01:27,834 --> 02:01:28,727
Actually,

1279
02:01:28,751 --> 02:01:30,518
the professor has
another version of the ending.

1280
02:01:30,542 --> 02:01:31,476
Professor.

1281
02:01:31,500 --> 02:01:32,842
Take a look.

1282
02:01:40,459 --> 02:01:41,717
Professor Fang.

1283
02:01:41,751 --> 02:01:46,134
Do you really have a better ending?

1284
02:01:46,834 --> 02:01:48,717
I have another ending

1285
02:02:33,167 --> 02:02:35,675
Mengyun would rather
sacrifice herself

1286
02:02:36,834 --> 02:02:38,759
to save your life.

1287
02:02:39,167 --> 02:02:41,425
I asked her before she died.

1288
02:02:42,167 --> 02:02:44,092
Knowing that you two
were not meant together,

1289
02:02:44,584 --> 02:02:47,092
why she insisted on doing that?

1290
02:02:52,375 --> 02:02:55,134
The day when we first met

1291
02:02:57,292 --> 02:02:59,342
he did not know me,

1292
02:03:01,584 --> 02:03:04,259
but he risked his life
to protect me.

1293
02:03:06,876 --> 02:03:09,383
General's sincere kindness,

1294
02:03:11,876 --> 02:03:14,592
Mengyun can never forget.

1295
02:03:15,459 --> 02:03:17,634
If I can just help him

1296
02:03:17,876 --> 02:03:20,759
to fulfill his wish in protecting
the country and people,

1297
02:03:22,125 --> 02:03:24,884
Mengyun dies with no regrets.

1298
02:03:58,500 --> 02:04:05,092
"The moon in the sky
changes its appearance"

1299
02:04:05,292 --> 02:04:10,842
"The autumn leaves fall unnoticed"

1300
02:04:12,125 --> 02:04:19,059
"The time travel seems
imaginary and yet so real"

1301
02:04:19,083 --> 02:04:26,059
"And you are as happy as
a good dream"

1302
02:04:26,083 --> 02:04:32,675
"The winter snow
stumbles its way here"

1303
02:04:32,999 --> 02:04:38,675
"Fragmentary memories
of many centuries"

1304
02:04:39,584 --> 02:04:46,602
"Devotion to be part of you
becomes lovesick"

1305
02:04:46,626 --> 02:04:53,351
"No one can separate you from me"

1306
02:04:53,375 --> 02:05:00,351
"This love is you, me,
mountains and the sea"

1307
02:05:00,375 --> 02:05:07,101
"It lasts to the present
and never falls apart"

1308
02:05:07,125 --> 02:05:10,727
"This love is you and me"

1309
02:05:10,751 --> 02:05:16,268
"my desire in this life"

1310
02:05:16,292 --> 02:05:20,976
"is to give it all for you"

1311
02:05:21,000 --> 02:05:24,185
"This love is what gives us"

1312
02:05:24,209 --> 02:05:29,975
"something from nothing
and our bonding"

1313
02:05:29,999 --> 02:05:35,425
"I will spend my life"

1314
02:05:37,083 --> 02:05:43,467
"waiting for you"

